    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am so excited to show you this absolute beauty! Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that you\u2019d swear it just rolled off the showroom floor. It has been totally pampered since day one\u2014the interior is spotless, the paint is gleaming, and it drives like a total dream. I've taken such good care of it, and I'm really looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. Feel free to reach out with any questions; I\u2019m happy to chat and show you why this is the perfect find! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
