      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is an investment-grade 2001 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine condition. This specimen features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp with a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline facilitated by individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double-VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring tactile engagement and linear power delivery. This example has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement to address known chassis harmonics. The suspension geometry remains true, with all bushings and dampers exhibiting factory-spec rebound and compression. Finished in its original pigment with zero oxidation or panel misalignment, this M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
