    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, scratches, or stone chips, recently protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Step inside to an interior that remains indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any bolster wear or creasing, and the cabin remains smoke-free and scent-neutral. Mechanically, this car is flawless. It comes with a complete, chronologically organized service history from the authorized dealership, with the most recent multi-point inspection and fluid service performed just 200 miles ago. The engine bay is remarkably clean, and the transmission shifts with factory-spec precision. It sits on brand-new Michelin tires mounted on flawless alloy wheels with no curb rash. This is a collector-grade vehicle for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection. Sale includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a custom-fit indoor car cover.",
      "price": 46500.0,
